column2: SELECT TOP #   p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,   p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,   p.petroMag_u, p.extinction_u,     p.petroMag_g, p.extinction_g,   p.petroMag_r, p.extinction_r,   p.petroMag_i, p.extinction_i,   p.petroMag_z, p.extinction_z,   s.specobjid, s.z,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr,      s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.instrument, s.survey, s.programname   INTO mydb.AGNControl_stripe8#   FROM Galaxy AS p      JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid      JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON gsl.specObjID = s.specObjID    WHERE (p.ra<#. or p.ra>#.) and (p.dec<# and p.dec>#) and p.mode = # and s.sciencePrimary = #      and s.class = &&& and p.petroMag_r-p.extinction_r<=#.
